sentence: Among the underlying components of the S&P 500 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Public Storage (Symbol: PSA), where a total of 9,361 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 936,100 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 126.6% of PSA's average daily trading volume over the past month of 739,575 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $230 strike call option expiring December 20, 2019, with 7,500 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 750,000 underlying shares of PSA.
